{"tid":1119465,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"阿Sa情慾戲支那版被刪    導演要賺支那錢又發聲明表震怒","createTime":"2019-04-22T02:55:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T03:20:05.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8837114095380a5d73d356cf6719361219f28ddd","tid":1119465,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T02:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/OCZSDXhXhaaBrVMBuNeELQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20190421f125833.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FOCZSDXhXhaaBrVMBuNeELQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20190421f125833.jpg&h=f88e5b85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】蔡卓妍（阿Sa）於電影《非分熟女》有大膽情慾及性感演出，阿Sa憑這片獲提名金像獎最佳女主角，宣傳時亦謂是從影以來最突破的演出。當中一場她親身上陣的出浴戲，雖然只是背部全裸出鏡，但正做著她表達慾望的動作，畫面大膽。但這原先90分鐘片長的公映版本，和108分鐘的導演版，於內地上映時卻被刪剩66分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n作為這片編劇兼導演的曾翠珊，就此於社交平台發「鄭重聲明」，「本人曾翠珊為《非分熟女》的導演及編劇，近日於國內播放修剪成66分鐘的版本，本人並沒有參與任何修剪程序，對於故事的原意完全被扭曲，感到震怒，以及極度的痛心。作為《非分熟女》的編導，本人只承認《非分熟女》的導演版（108 min）及公映版（90 min）為本人參與的創作。」網民對此不以為奇，留言「內地不嬲係咁剪」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E9%98%BFsa%E6%83%85%E6%85%BE%E6%88%B2%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%89%88%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%AA-%E5%B0%8E%E6%BC%94%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E%E8%A1%A8%E9%9C%87%E6%80%92-045000408.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.celebrity.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2598%25BFsa%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%2585%25BE%25E6%2588%25B2%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2589%2588%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2588%25AA-%25E5%25B0%258E%25E6%25BC%2594%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E9%259C%2587%25E6%2580%2592-045000408.html&d=1KnBewcMxCifpJVTRQbR6qZPNspveiVXvfzVSLwjqls%3D&h=2892bbef\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E9%98%BFsa%E6%83%85%E6%85%BE%E6%88%B2%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%89%88%E8%